window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Marry once for duty. Marry twice for obsession.</b></p> <p>I was meant for more than teaching psychology at Blackmore University. I am the second son of the family's consigliere. They married me to a widow who quickly passed. My inheritanceâ€”her daughter.</p> <p>I admit that I have looked favorably upon her over the years. I admit that intentions have been less than noble.</p> <p>Now, she's at Blackmore. Away from the family's watchful eyes. Away from her uncles who see right through me. Away from everything that keeps us apart.</p> <p>They call our love forbidden. I call it endgame.</p> <p><i>Dark romance author Cora Kent brings you a forbidden romance between a college professor and the student he's spent the last five years fantasizing about. </i>Dark Obsession<i> is Niccolo and Christine's story. This novel features dark themes, steamy scenes, and mature content. Each book in the Blackmore University series can be enjoyed as a standalone.</i></p>"; 
